{"tid":1841531,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"衛生署有需要時會用未入伙粉嶺暉明邨做隔離","createTime":"2020-01-25T09:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T23:30:30.000Z","uid":10540,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5cf511c7445b9e6df674c8c4eaf5349ee9953e","tid":1841531,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/26kFLOBQgWY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F26kFLOBQgWY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=4d2b68cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衛生署長陳漢儀表示，已開始在高鐵西九龍站試用電子健康申報系統，希望稍後可以引入到其他口岸。她又說，已開始聯絡各非政府團體，借用渡假村作隔離用途，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">亦會改裝未入伙的粉嶺公屋邨暉明邨，讓確診個案的緊密接觸者或有需要的醫護人員入住。</span></strong>陳漢儀說，理解有前線醫護人員不想放工後返回住所，政府會與酒店業界研究租用酒店給醫護人員入住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255898&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1255898%26csid%3D261_341&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=64a08bb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255898&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6317aa9baee8967ace4606c04b2dd390b77d5e09","tid":1841531,"uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTQEjKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTQEjKC.jpg&h=9ffbc21a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d180732274fb74fd14c2ccecfeabf1d367535a9","tid":1841531,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"04b39ca776b179af64f66da2732d52cc6fb831f3","tid":1841531,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"用啓晴邨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b9184364eef412e3f4e0d2650b3a10a1f13671",